title: How did i get unranked?? [Was Plat 4]
body: I stopped playing league of like 2 weeks came back to an unranked account... how did this happen?

replies.body: This is a display issue while we are undergoing maintenance.   We'll be posting updates on our [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page.   It will return to normal after!
if you would take the time to read the service announcement in the top right you would know the Leagues System is down right now
